itemDescription: English racing cyclist, cycling coach and cycling journalist

wikipedia_page.main: Russell Williams (born 14 April 1961) is an English former professional road and track cyclist from London. Williams is also a cycling coach and David Duffield's co-commentator on Eurosport.
